    "biasType": "Opinion Statements Presented as Fact",
    "biasedText": "Many Democrats on Capitol Hill saw the October-to-November shutdown as a political success. It put Democrats' top issue of health care costs at the top of the national political agenda, and most voters blamed Republicans more than Democrats for the shutdown.",
    "explanation": "While the first sentence attributes the 'political success' assessment to Democrats, the second sentence presents as fact that the shutdown 'put Democrats' top issue... at the top of the national political agenda' without attribution or evidence. This is a causal and strategic judgment presented as objective reality."
